<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,151,1005]" box="[199,732,943,968]" pageId="6" pageNumber="224">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,943,968]" pageId="6" pageNumber="224">Distribution.</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[359,434,943,968]" name="Russia" pageId="6" pageNumber="224">Russia</collectingCountry>
(Tuva, Republic of Altai).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,151,1005]" box="[199,1283,980,1005]" pageId="6" pageNumber="224">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,299,980,1005]" pageId="6" pageNumber="224">Ecology.</emphasis>
Inhabits steppe areas, where occurs in sandy and forest biotopes along rivers and lakes.
</paragraph>
